Compilation Instructions
------------------------

To compile both serial and parallel versions:

    make

This generates two executables:

    kmeans-serial
    kmeans-parallel


To remove executables:

    make clean


Running Instructions
--------------------

1. Serial Version

Usage:

    ./kmeans-serial -s <number_objects> -k <number_clusters>

Example:

    ./kmeans-serial -s 10000 -k 4


2. Parallel Version

Usage:

    ./kmeans-parallel -s <number_objects> -k <number_clusters> -n <number_threads>

Example:

    ./kmeans-parallel -s 10000 -k 4 -n 8



Test Parameters
----------------

1) <number_objects> = [10000, 100000, 1000000]
2) <number_clusters> = [2, 4, 8, 16]
3) <number_threads> = [1, 2, 4, 8, 16, 32, 64]
